## Getting Started

Clone project

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Patcharadnaimingchua/user-management-api.git
cd user-management-api
```

Run project

```bash
docker compose up --build
```

API

```
http://localhost:3000
```

Swagger

```
http://localhost:3000/api-docs
```

---

## Environment Variables

```env
PORT=3000
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://appuser:changeme@db:5432/userdb

JWT_SECRET=supersecret
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=15m
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d
```

---

## Database

Migration

```bash
docker exec -it node_app npx prisma migrate deploy
```

Seed

```bash
docker exec -it node_app npx prisma db seed
```

---

## Testing

```bash
docker exec -it node_app npm test
```

